One thing for sure in this life—time passes. Babies get big, relationships change, people move, we get old. Life shifts. J sent this video last night. It made me tear up. SO MUCH has changed and in the moment the video was taken I’m sure it felt like nothing would ever change. We aren’t what we once were, but we will ALWAYS, always be a family. This is just a reminder that your life doesn’t have to look like anybody else’s and enjoy all the moments.
